         <p>These materials have been arranged and described according to national and local standards. For more information, please refer to the Beinecke Manuscript Unit Processing Manual.</p>
         <p>Former call numbers: Z117 068d, Z117 068e.</p>
      </processinfo>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_dec14b577fc9ea802614da8c33fd5dec">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Manuscript account books and daybooks of Jonathan Knight listing patients of his medical practice in New Haven, Connecticut, 1813-1864.</p>
      </scopecontent>
